    "title": "Proposal: be able to change the location of the blockchain data for Bitcoin core client",
    "body": "People need to change the location of the blockchain data to some other place(Other disk/partition/folder, etc) before running out the disk capacity. \n\nIt is now not support to do this in Bitcoin Core 0.9.2.1. \n\nIt would be great to allow people to set / customise the location of the blockchain data. For both during the installation & after installation.\n",
